Are you still hype from watching The Suicide Squad and want to quench your thirst for zany action and colorful characters? Lucky for you WB released a slightly similar and underrated film in 2010 based off the Vertigo comic series of the same name; The Losers! With a cast that is basically comic book movie royalty in 2021, watch the film that is a product of its time while setting the table for other assemble action comedies of the future! Grab your grenade launcher, get ready to hack the mainframe, and let's dance in this review of The Losers!

